Package: sardine
Type: Package
Title: Structured Architecture for Research Data Integration and Evaluation
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Jack", "Manners", email = "jack.manners@flinders.edu.au", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An R package providing a structured interface for research data integration
    and evaluation, with initial focus on REDCap API integration. The package facilitates
    secure and efficient data exchange between R and various research data platforms.
